     Data & Research - This area contains quarterly industry information,
     statistical reports and studies of interest to the industry.

     Industry Performance - Includes the quarterly press conference
     industry charts and financial highlights.

     Corporate Directories - Includes searchable databases of
     institutions and holding companies.

     Statistical Releases - Includes cost of funds indices,
     asset/liability price tables, and other statistical information.

     Studies and Papers - Includes research papers published by our
     agency on topics including the mortgage market, risk management, and
     other financial issues.


